OL,3,CCorrie actress Sally Lindsay to
OL,4,Creceive honours at Windsor
OL,6,FFormer Coronation Street star Sally
OL,7,FLindsay will be among 67 people given
OL,8,Fhonours by the Prince of Wales.
OL,10,FLindsay, who is best known for playing
OL,11,Fthe Rovers Return landlady Shelley
OL,12,FUnwin on the ITV soap, was made a
OL,13,FMember of the Order of the British
OL,14,FEmpire (MBE) in the King's New Year
OL,15,FHonours for her services to drama.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
