OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782290900
OL,3,CCorrie actress Sally Lindsay to
OL,4,Creceive honours at Windsor
OL,6,FThe 52-year-old actress starred on
OL,7,FCorrie from 2001 until 2006, with her
OL,8,Fcharacter's biggest storylines
OL,9,Fincluding being at the centre of the
OL,10,Fpsychological and physical abuse of
OL,11,Fher boyfriend, Charlie Stubbs, played
OL,12,Fby Bill Ward, whom she eventually
OL,13,Fleaves at the altar.
OL,15,FThe role won her the Inside Soap award
OL,16,Ffor best actress in 2005.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
