OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782290900
OL,3,CCorrie actress Sally Lindsay to
OL,4,Creceive honours at Windsor
OL,6,FIn 2011, she co-created and starred in
OL,7,FITV's Scott & Bailey, alongside
OL,8,FSuranne Jones and Lesley Sharp, about
OL,9,Ftwo detectives specialising in murder
OL,10,Fcases at a Manchester police unit.
OL,12,FShe went on to star in Sky sitcom
OL,13,FMount Pleasant from 2011 until 2017
OL,14,Fbefore appearing in Cold Call, a crime
OL,15,Fdrama about a single mother who
OL,16,Fbecomes a victim of fraud.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
