PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782290900
OL,3,CCorrie actress Sally Lindsay to
OL,4,Creceive honours at Windsor
OL,6,FShe more recently co-created and
OL,7,Fstarred in the Channel 5 drama, The
OL,8,FMadame Blanc Mysteries, about a
OL,9,FBritish antiques dealer who solves
OL,10,Fmysteries in the south of France.
OL,12,FSally will receive her honours at an
OL,13,Finvestiture ceremony at Windsor Castle
OL,14,Fon Wednesday, 25 June.
